node.text:
Looking at our page, it’s obvious that we love chonky boys. And if you’re following us, you probably love them too! ❤️

That’s why we’re excited to tell you about our friends over at The Chonkz 💕

Right now they have this crazy BUY 1 GET 1 FREE sale 😍 
 
You have unique chance to get those cute chonky guys for less than ever ✨

For the next 48h❗
For @round.boys followers only:
BUY 1 GET 1 FREE SALE!!!🔥

Check out the link in our bio @round.boys and get your chonkz with FREE SHIPPING 🌟

#sale #chonky #thechonkz
